flowchart LR
  U[User] --> A[Agent Orchestrator]
  A --> P[Planner (LLM)
  produces proposed plan JSON]
  P -->|plan JSON| E[Executor (Deterministic)
  trust boundary]

  E -->|validate + normalize| V{Schema + policy
  checks pass?}
  V -- No --> R[Reject w/ reasons
  ask LLM to regenerate] --> P
  V -- Yes --> T[Tool Adapter] --> S[Service / DB / External APIs]

  S --> T --> E
  E --> A --> U
